0:

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ambient forest sounds
des: Let the sounds of an ambient forest, full of woodland creatures thrust you into a deep sleep. Ambient Forest Sounds is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. \n\nAll you need to do is say Alexa start Ambient Forest Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
